name: Witnesses
overview: A young female detective is put in charge of a case and must delve into her partner's mysterious past in order to solve it.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Detective Sandra Winckler follows a bizarre clue to begin unraveling a ghastly crime perpetrated in a model home.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Winckler gets a new partner, veteran detective Paul Maisonneuve, but she soon suspects that someone from his past is out to settle an old score.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: In the model home, Detectives Winckler and Maisonneuve uncover evidence that Kaz Gorbier is still alive, but is he the man they're looking for?

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: When Kaz Gorbier takes hostages and flees, Detective Maisonneuve sets out after him -- but Gorbier has a few dirty tricks up his sleeve.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: With the clock ticking, Detective Winckler sets out to save her partner, Detective Maisonneuve, from the clutches of Kaz Gorbier.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Detective Maisonneuve discovers the culprit responsible for the harassment he has suffered and its grim connection to the unearthed bodies.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: 15 passengers are found frozen to death in a bus. They wear festive clothes, but did not know each other. Sandra Winckler starts an investigation.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Where did the bus come from? A man frozen to death and a missing woman who just had a baby. The case reminds Officer Winckler of a case ten years ago.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: At a wind turbine, the body of a young woman who just gave birth is found. Sandra believes another bus will be found in the surrounding area.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: For safety reasons, Sandra may be taken off the case. She refuses to step down. Catherine thinks she found the killer, but Sandra is not so sure.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Antoine is kidnapped, probably by the unknown killer. Sandra and Catherine devise a plan to get Martin Souriau to lead them to the killer.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Sandra investigates the orphanage where the killer lived as a child. She has a list of names and decides to track all children down.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Sandra is captured by the killer, who wants to 'marry’ her. The ceremony consists of killing her previous partners and lovers.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: In the season finale, all questions are answered. Can Sandra prevent the wedding? Will Catherine find her missing baby? And who is the Minotaur?
